==Russian==

===Preposition===
'''об''' ''(before vowels)'', [[о#Russian|о]] ''(before consonants)'', [[обо]] ''(before some difficult consonant clusters such as '''''мн-''''' and '''''вс-''''')''

#''(+ [[prepositional case]])'': [[about]], [[of]], [[on]]
#:*{{RUchar|Они́ [[говорить|говоря́т]] обо [[я#Russian|мне́]]}} — ''They are talking about me.''
#:*{{RUchar|[[Я]] [[читать|чита́л]] о [[он|нём]]}} — ''I read about him.''
#''(+ [[accusative case]])'': [[against]], [[upon]]
#:*{{RUchar|[[опираться|опира́ться]] о [[стена|сте́ну]]}} — ''to lean against the wall''

